overview: Join the Lucas Men as they compete for the honor of “Breeding Prince Charming”, with Brian Bonds as the star of the show! A cast of hot and horny contestants starring Marq Daniels, Sergeant Miles, Rico Marlon, Damon Heart, Andrey Vic, and Adam Killian compete, plot, suck, rim, and fuck their way to the finish line. Who will beat out all the other guys and earn the grand prize of Brian Bonds for a night of “Breeding Prince Charming”?
title: Breeding Prince Charming
